Package: schemar
Title: Build Structured Data Frame Subtypes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Cory", "McCartan", , "mccartan@psu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6251-669X"))
Description: Provides developer-focused helper functions and S3 classes to ease
    the creation of structured subtypes of data frames which require certain columns
    and types to be present, and which preserve special attributes through common
    data frame manipulations.
